.SH "RELOADING THE CONFIGURATION"
.HP \w'\fBcommand\fR\ 'u
\fBcommand\fR [options]
.PP
Use the
\fBsyslog\-ng\-ctl reload\fR
command to reload the configuration file of without having to restart the application\&. The
\fBsyslog\-ng\-ctl reload\fR
works like a SIGHUP\&.
